{"tid":1975791,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人大炎上日本Vtuber失敗","createTime":"2020-04-16T19:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T04:36:54.000Z","uid":172738,"like":87,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d04cb6d9d046f2b31824ea53b0fa2b2e5553c6","tid":1975791,"uid":172738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iasrBye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiasrBye.jpg&h=0f8e7390&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n好事成雙<br />\n要講既係上圖左兔田字幕組<br />\n<br />\n大概兩日前,有個叫兎田ぺこら既日本vtuber係twitter轉貼左一條niconico既片,話好好笑<br />\n但條片原本係bilibili支那人整既,比人轉載去niconico<br />\n兎田ぺこら係bilibili既字幕組因為轉貼條片,令一班支那人激到扎扎跳<br />\n話條片係偷既,佢轉貼即係支持偷野<br />\n話佢唔尊重支那人,要求佢去bilibili直播道歉<br />\n字幕組就係度刪留言,激化件事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb1TgBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb1TgBL.jpg&h=048d75b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一時間貼吧班anti好似執到寶咁,想借機搞大件事<br />\n瘋狂帶風向,為左趕走班vtuber出中國市場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://swallow.5ch.net/test/read.cgi/livejupiter/1586899206/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fswallow.5ch.net%2Ftest%2Fread.cgi%2Flivejupiter%2F1586899206%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=87726123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://swallow.5ch.net/test/read.cgi/livejupiter/1586899206/</a><br />\n另一方面係日本vtuber anti集中地既5ch<br />\n一大班日本網民對e件事表示完全唔明燒乜野<br />\n仲係度恥笑<br />\n部份留言<br />\nbilibili先係偷開片<br />\n原來支那人有版權意識?<br />\n侵權既人仲主張佢有版權?面皮真係厚<br />\n支那人有冇問過人地公司先用人地既野呀?<br />\n即係中國無印告日本無印?<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n隔左一日,事主再開直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cpRii7C2krQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcpRii7C2krQ&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=9821b8aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cpRii7C2krQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sP3FFoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsP3FFoM.jpg&h=3596ccc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGakF7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGakF7Q.jpg&h=b6929e64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係直播期間雖然有少量支那人洗板叫佢道歉<br />\n但大量支持者用行動(donate)黎支持兔田,1場直播總共收約300萬yen(平時有活動先可能做到1次直播有100萬yen,1個月計埋都未必有好多人做到)<br />\n兼1萬like(平時3~4千)<br />\n至於dislike,日本anti出動都可能有4,5千甚至更多<br />\n但今次由於日本anti反應唔熱烈,計埋中國翻到牆既水軍<br />\n總共得1300 dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nnga專版雖然都有人帶風向,但受惠gbf事件成個壇收皮<br />\nanti只可以轉戰bilibili<br />\n<br />\n最新發展狗咬狗<br />\n支那fans vs 貼吧+anti"},{"pid":"e7a3edeac304dbf3eea5ff02f69dda2391032ccb","tid":1975791,"uid":165711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:35:17.000Z","msg":"内鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1ac77f1d696fb81ae80f0a433b1f6c4a49ed90","tid":1975791,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T20:34:18.000Z","msg":"推爆<br />\n支那人醜事就係要畀更多人知"},{"pid":"0c74210087b05a03da23ff84ed6b8efaf0265af9","tid":1975791,"uid":24163,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T20:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5j2asX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5j2asX.gif&h=6a337cb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5a53769770c03c97d21cb7df843a5a82b75ac38","tid":1975791,"uid":24163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T20:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwYN51Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwYN51Z.gif&h=90a9bdf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f359b01c196