791,"uid":90521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a3d0f338173b49b235b83fd0309d74f07c6a8b3","tid":1975791,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:15:35.000Z","msg":"但係個vtuber都跪左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"咁諗，佢出道歉聲明基本上緊既<br />\n問題就係出完之後佢重會唔會去b站開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本成單野nmslese目標有冇達成都係輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b03124c4e2a3bf6173553da6aec319f2754b47","tid":1975791,"uid":110832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"完全唔知噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ae1d5d3fe0fa1b89b8400c264be67c87c1931","tid":1975791,"uid":6752,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"00b03124c4e2a3bf6173553da6aec319f2754b47","tid":1975791,"uid":110832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"完全唔知噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"簡單講咪有心人想借愛國心黎煽動d人反日，例牌你唔尊重中國，逼人道歉<br />\n但牆內開頭都有d反應，去到牆外就收左皮<br />\n人地日本人包括hater係e件事都選擇唔幫支那人<br />\n睇詳情仲多terms,外人應該仲難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論就係支那人出精失敗，返到狗籠又比其他狗咬<br />\n官方d都只係出官腔回應，冇跟佢地要求"},{"pid":"6bae298a5fd7ba93a04e4ae76a8c203baae38311","tid":1975791,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"燒起來了燒起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那賤畜連非商業二創既轉載都包容唔到<br />\n咁都好燒 笑撚死我"},{"pid":"0bf0e78c490812f56393bc1fa3fde6a83144c8e8","tid":1975791,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:44:29.000Z","msg":"日本Vtuber呢行近呢一兩年奶共(bilibili)奶得幾犀利下<br />\n